'''''Mandabi''''' (Igifaransa: '''''Le Mandat''''', "The Money Order") ni filime yo mu 1968 yanditswe kandi iyobowe n'umukinnyi wa filime wo muri Senegali Ousmane Sembène <ref>https://www.theguardian.com/film/2021/jun/09/mandabi-review-ousmane-sembene-senegal</ref>. Iyi filime ishingiye ku gitabo cya Sembène cyitwa ''The Money-Order'' kandi ni filime ya mbere y’umuyobozi mu rurimi rwe kavukire rwa Wolof <ref>https://www.criterion.com/films/29067-mandabi</ref>. Kubera ko benshi mu baturage ba Senegal batumva igifaransa, Sembène yashakaga guhanga sinema kubavuga Wolof<ref>https://www.criterionchannel.com/mandabi</ref>. Iyi niyo filime ya mbere yuzuye  ururimi nyafurika kuva muri Afrika y'uburengerazuba<ref>https://www.independentcinemaoffice.org.uk/films/mandabi/</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Umuyisilamu wo muri Senegal udafite akazi, Ibrahima Dieng, abana n'abagore be babiri n'abana barindwi i Dakar <ref>https://www.bfi.org.uk/sight-and-sound/reviews/mandabi-1968-ousmane-sembene-restored-wolof-masterwork</ref>. Mwishywa we, Abdou, yohereje we kugira amafaranga kuva Paris agaciro 25.000 y'amanyarwanda<ref>https://www.sff.org.au/program/browse/mandabi</ref>, akaba yarakijjwe no gukubura mu muhanda<ref>Ousmane Sembene - Mandabi <nowiki>https://www.mtholyoke.edu</nowiki> › page20</ref>. Ibrahima akabika amafaranga ye wenyine, akazigamira mwishywa we, agaha mushiki we umugabane<ref>https://www.sff.org.au/program/browse/mandabi</ref>.

== Kwandika ==
Nyuma yuko iyi filime itari imaze imyaka igera ku bantu bareba sinema, yasubiwemo mu mwanzuro wa 4K maze itangwa mu iserukiramuco rya Lumière rya 2019 ryabereye i Lyon mu Bufaransa.  Muri Kamena 2021, iyi verisiyo yasubiwemo yerekanwe muri sinema mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]]<ref>https://www.britannica.com/topic/Mandabi</ref> .

